The paper discusses the use of robots in surgery, which involves the integration of robotics, artificial intelligence, computer vision, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics and Automation), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
